Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:04.69,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,僕は　頭がおかしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:08.66,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,山田杏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.74,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,一体何なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.33,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やれやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.03,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:13.87,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:14.83,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,何なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:15.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,よかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:16.45,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.25,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,何なんだ　あの女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:25.96,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ねればねるほど　色が変わって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:27.55,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:28.76,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,違うだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.26,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いいにおいするやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:31.76,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,しないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:33.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.56,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,僕と山田は　まったく違う世界の人間なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.40,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんか　知らない女の人みたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.65,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,市川って　面白いね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.86,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,くだらない　何もかもがどうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:50.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,市川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.03,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうでもいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:54.49,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,これでいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:55.12,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,嘘でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:55.83,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そんな人生なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:56.58,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どう思う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:57.50,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:00:58.45,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,楽しいと思うな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.46,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうでもいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:00:59.91,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:00.96,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうでもいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:01.50,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ね？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:02.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:10.26,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:12.18,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,最初から分かっていただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:12.55,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,分かれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:13.59,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,本当は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.43,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,約束だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:15.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今までが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:16.31,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:17.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.39,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.81,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,気持ちが　伝わりそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:22.73,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:23.60,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:25.61,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,本当は欲しくてたまらないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:26.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,僕が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:27.73,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうせ手に入らないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:28.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,こんなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:35.70,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,僕は　{\alpha&HFF&\t(3120,3121,\alpha&H00&)\fad(500,0)}山田が好きなんだ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue Chinese
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.15,0:00:04.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我腦子不正常
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.20,0:00:08.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田杏奈
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真費勁
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.03,0:00:13.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.87,0:00:14.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.83,0:00:15.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,做了好事呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.95,0:00:16.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這女人怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.38,0:00:25.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,越攪拌… 顏色變化越大
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.51,0:00:27.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.55,0:00:28.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我在幹嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這是那種有香氣的扇子啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.59,0:00:31.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.30,0:00:33.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有哦
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我和山田 就好像活在不同世界裡的人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她彷彿搖身一變 成了另一個人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市川 你真有意思
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.86,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,無趣 什麼都是無所謂的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.86,0:00:50.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市川
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不關我事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.32,0:00:54.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.49,0:00:55.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你撒謊了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.12,0:00:55.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我人生也就這樣了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.83,0:00:56.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.58,0:00:57.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,關我什麼事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.50,0:00:58.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我覺得還挺開心的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,和我沒關係啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.46,0:00:59.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你聞聞
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.91,0:01:00.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這關我什麼事啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.96,0:01:01.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.96,0:01:02.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.09,0:01:10.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.59,0:01:12.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我從一開始不就該明白了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.18,0:01:12.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,快明白吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.80,0:01:13.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,說好了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.43,0:01:15.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,至今
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.10,0:01:16.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.31,0:01:17.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,全都
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感情 就要迸發出來了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.81,0:01:22.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好害怕
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.73,0:01:23.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但即便如此
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.60,0:01:25.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我分明是那麼想要得到
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.61,0:01:26.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.07,0:01:27.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,卻總以反正不歸我為藉口
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.73,0:01:28.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是那麼
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.70,0:01:35.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,原來 {\alpha&HFF&\t(3120,3121,\alpha&H00&)\fad(500,0)}我喜歡山田啊
